achieving.from sentence: The proposed method , denoted by WSD - TM in the tables referring to WSD using topic models , outperforms the state - of - the - art WSD system by a significant margin ( pvalue < 0.01 ) by achieving an overall F1 - score of 66.9 as compared to Moro14 's score of 65.5 .
